snippet.title: Horizon Forbidden West Complete Edition - Launch Accolades Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Follow the next chapter of Aloy's journey as she braves the Forbidden West – a majestic but dangerous frontier that conceals mysterious new threats - and beyond, to the ruins of Los Angeles into a treacherous archipelago.

See what the critics are saying about Horizon Forbidden West and Horizon Forbidden West: Burning Shores.

Learn more here: https://www.playstation.com/games/horizon-forbidden-west/
